  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Irish Aid HPP 2016</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CA Ireland 2016 allocation from Irish Aid&apos;s Humanitarian Programme Plan (HPP). There are 4 projects under the 2016 HPP: South Kivu, DRC (12 months); Unity State, South Sudan (12 months); Makamba Province, Burundi (12 months) and Bekaa region, Lebanon (12 months). The HPP provides funding for protracted, predictable and recurring humanitarian crises. The projects address the short and longer-term needs of conflict-affected populations, with a particular focus on gender and protection.</narrative>
  </description>
